**Summary**: Added `write_status_snapshot()` to `ProjectService` that writes `data/status.json` after each agent run. The snapshot includes:
- Project health (RAG status, forecast end, sponsor)
- Metrics (task counts by status, overdue count, RAID/action summaries)
- Milestone statuses with planned/forecast/actual dates
- Individual task details (status, priority, due date, blockers, dependencies)

Wired into `agent.py` so it runs automatically after the LangGraph loop completes, before the reference date advances.
